            </tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>
      <p class="mt-3 text-xs italic text-ink-500">Prices as of June 2026; verify current. All prices exclude 18% GST. QuickBooks India closed to new subscriptions (service ended 30 April 2023).</p>
      <p class="mt-6 text-[15px] leading-relaxed text-ink-700"><strong>The honest take:</strong> if you only need occasional e-way bills, the free government e-way bill portal works directly. But for businesses moving goods regularly, generating <strong>e-way bills and e-invoices from the same invoice, linked to live stock, with unlimited users on one flat bill</strong> saves real time — and that is where <strong>Nidhi Books from ₹399/month</strong> (plus <a class="text-brand-700 hover:underline" href="/apps/inventory/">Nidhi Inventory</a> for stock) is the best-value choice.</p>
